character.name: Warrior

character.name: Rogue
character.description: A truly deceptive being from the Coast of Atla, she attacks with blinding speed and accuracy.!Primary Stat: Strength!Damage Type: Physical

character.name: Mage
character.description: It deals in the dark arts of blood magic and sorcery as the screams of suffering souls emanate from its staff.!Primary Stat: Intelligence!Damage Type: Magic

character.name: Healer
character.description: Her healing techniques are unmatched and make her a key ally in batte, but she is relatively unarmed.!Primary Stat: Will!Damage Type: Magic

character.name: Archer
character.description: His tightly-strung bow shoots various arrows while his trusty horn enables him to call on animal spirits in defense.!Primary Stats: Agility, Intelligence!Damage Types: Ranged, Magic
